From DrGeo image, with Gettext package installed, execute:

     TextDomainManager registerCategoryPrefix: 'DrGeo/Core' domain: 'drgeo/drgeocore'.
      
     GetTextExporter exportTemplate.

To see the locale and locale directories, in the DrGeo image:

     Locale determineCurrentLocale
     GetTextTranslator defaultLocaleDirs

Beware, carriage return (CR) are \r in the messages, keep it like
this.
